Tens of thousands of Malaysians rally in the capital Kuala Lumpur calling for Prime Minister Najib Razak to step down over a financial scandal where a MYR 2.672 billion (USD 700 million) payment was made to his bank account from unnamed foreign donors. (BBC News)Voting for the second round of Benin's election begins with current President Thomas Boni Yayi stepping down after completing two terms. (Townhall via Reuters)